                "invention-title": [
                    "Heat exchange regeneration gas purification device and method",
                    "一种换热再生气体纯化装置及其方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a heat exchange regenerated gas purification device and method. The heat exchange regenerated gas purification device comprises a gas inlet assembly, a deoxidation heat exchanger is fixed to one end of the gas inlet assembly, a deaerator is connected to the gas outlet end of a heater, a regeneration heat exchanger is arranged at one end of the deaerator, and the deoxidation heat exchanger and the regeneration heat exchanger are oppositely communicated and introduced into a cooling assembly; and a drying assembly is arranged on one side of the cooling assembly. By detecting the temperature of raw material hydrogen at the outlet of the deoxidation heat exchanger and the temperature of regeneration gas at the outlet of the regeneration heat exchanger, the automatic valve and the regulating valve are controlled to be opened and closed, and the raw material gas entering the deoxidizer and the regeneration gas entering the dryer in the regeneration state are heated by heat released by reaction of hydrogen and oxygen in the deoxidizer. The working time of the electric heater can be shortened, deoxidized hydrogen is cooled through heat exchange, the temperature of an inlet of the raw material normal-temperature cooler is reduced, under the condition that the temperature of an outlet is not changed, the cooling water consumption of the raw material normal-temperature cooler is reduced, the working time of the electric heater is shortened, and therefore the electric energy consumption of the device is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请涉及一种换热再生气体纯化装置及其方法，包括有进气组件，进气组件一端固定有脱氧换热器，加热器出气端连接有脱氧器，脱氧器一端设置有再生换热器，脱氧换热器与再生换热器相对连通且通入冷却组件的内部，冷却组件的一侧设置有干燥组件。本申请通过检测脱氧换热器出口原料氢气温度和再生换热器出口再生气温度，控制自动阀和调节阀开关，利用脱氧器中氢气和氧气反应放出热量加热进入脱氧器的原料气和进入处于再生状态的干燥器的再生气。本申请可减少电加热器的工作时间，脱氧氢气经过换热降温，降低了原料常温冷却器入口处温度，在出口温度不变情况下，减少了原料常温冷却器的冷却水用量，减少电加热器的工作时间，从而降低装置的电能耗。"
                }
            ]
